2026-04-14 18:11:46,039 | INFO | app | Processing email 19d8b191f8f63f7a content: {'subject': 'Due tomorrow: "Assignment (Unit–IV)SSMDA"', 'sender': '"Swernima Suman (Classroom)" <no-reply@classroom.google.com>', 'body': "Notification settings \n<https://accounts.google.com/AccountChooser?continue=https://classroom.google.com/s?email%3Dmh116727@gmail.com&Email=mh116727@gmail.com>\n3rd year T15 \n<https://accounts.google.com/AccountChooser?continue=https://classroom.google.com/c/ODQxNDY4MTAxOTc5?email%3Dmh116727@gmail.com&Email=mh116727@gmail.com>\nDue tomorrow\n\nAssignment (Unit–IV)SSMDA\nAssignment (Unit–IV)\n\nQ1. Define a vector space.\nVerify whether the set with usual addition and scalar multiplication forms \na vector space.\n\nQ2.\nDefine a subspace.\nTest whether the set\n\nW = \\{(x, y, z) \\in \\mathbb{R}^3 \\mid x + y + z = 0\\}\n\nQ3.\nExplain the concepts of basis and dimension of a vector space.\nFind the basis and dimension of the space:\n\nV = \\text{Span}\\{(1,0,0), (0,1,0), (0,0,1)\\}\n\nQ4. Define eigenvalues and eigenvectors.\nFind the eigenvalues of the matrix:\n\nA = \\begin{bmatrix} 2 & 0 \\\\ 0 & 3 \\end{bmatrix}\nDue Apr 15\nView assignment \n<https://accounts.google.com/AccountChooser?continue=https://classroom.google.com/c/ODQxNDY4MTAxOTc5/a/ODQ5MDEwOTkzNjQ3/submissions/by-status/and-sort-last-name/all?email%3Dmh116727@gmail.com&Email=mh116727@gmail.com>\n\nGoogle LLC 1600 Amphitheatre Parkway, Mountain View, CA 94043 USA\nThis email was sent to you because you indicated that you'd like to receive \nemail notifications from Google Classroom. If you don't want to receive \nemails like this, you can unsubscribe or change your settings \n<https://accounts.google.com/AccountChooser?continue=https://classroom.google.com/s?email%3Dmh116727@gmail.com&Email=mh116727@gmail.com>.", 'attachments': {}}
