2026-04-14 18:30:16,782 | INFO | app | Processing email 19d8b199ca509b1e content: {'subject': 'Due tomorrow: "UNIT–II Assignment(IT PROJECT MANAGEMENT)\r\n*Do any 3 question"', 'sender': '"Swernima Suman (Classroom)" <no-reply@classroom.google.com>', 'body': "Notification settings \n<https://accounts.google.com/AccountChooser?continue=https://classroom.google.com/s?email%3Dmh116727@gmail.com&Email=mh116727@gmail.com>\n3rd year T15 \n<https://accounts.google.com/AccountChooser?continue=https://classroom.google.com/c/ODQxNDY4MTAxOTc5?email%3Dmh116727@gmail.com&Email=mh116727@gmail.com>\nDue tomorrow\n\nUNIT–II Assignment(IT PROJECT MANAGEMENT)\n*Do any 3 question\nUNIT–II Assignment\nQ1. (a) What is Project Integration Management? Explain its importance in \nIT projects.\n\nQ1. (b) Describe the steps involved in Developing a Project Charter.\n\nQ2. (a) Explain the process of Developing a Project Management Plan in \ndetail.\n\nQ2. (b) What is Integrated Change Control? Why is it important?\n\nQ3. (a) What is Project Scope Management? Explain its key processes.\n\nQ3. (b) Define Work Breakdown Structure (WBS) and explain how it is created.\n\nQ4. (a) Explain the process of Collecting Requirements and Defining Scope.\n\nQ4. (b) What is Scope Verification and Scope Control? Explain with examples.\nDue Apr 15\nView assignment \n<https://accounts.google.com/AccountChooser?continue=https://classroom.google.com/c/ODQxNDY4MTAxOTc5/a/ODE5NDEzNjQzMjY4/submissions/by-status/and-sort-last-name/all?email%3Dmh116727@gmail.com&Email=mh116727@gmail.com>\n\nGoogle LLC 1600 Amphitheatre Parkway, Mountain View, CA 94043 USA\nThis email was sent to you because you indicated that you'd like to receive \nemail notifications from Google Classroom. If you don't want to receive \nemails like this, you can unsubscribe or change your settings \n<https://accounts.google.com/AccountChooser?continue=https://classroom.google.com/s?email%3Dmh116727@gmail.com&Email=mh116727@gmail.com>.", 'attachments