2026-04-14 18:40:59,609 | INFO | app | Processing email 19d8b1c1c0fcb0ea content: {'subject': 'Due tomorrow: "Assignment – Unit IV (IT)"', 'sender': '"Swernima Suman (Classroom)" <no-reply@classroom.google.com>', 'body': "Notification settings \n<https://accounts.google.com/AccountChooser?continue=https://classroom.google.com/s?email%3Dmh116727@gmail.com&Email=mh116727@gmail.com>\n3rd year T15 \n<https://accounts.google.com/AccountChooser?continue=https://classroom.google.com/c/ODQxNDY4MTAxOTc5?email%3Dmh116727@gmail.com&Email=mh116727@gmail.com>\nDue tomorrow\n\nAssignment – Unit IV (IT)\nAssignment – Unit IV\nQ1.\nWhat is Project Quality Management? Explain Quality Planning, Quality \nAssurance, and Quality Control with examples.\nQ2.\nDiscuss the role of Human Resource Management in projects. Explain how a \nproject team is acquired, developed, and managed.\nQ3.\nExplain Project Risk Management. Describe the process of identifying, \nanalyzing, and responding to risks in IT projects.\nDue Apr 15\nView assignment \n<https://accounts.google.com/AccountChooser?continue=https://classroom.google.com/c/ODQxNDY4MTAxOTc5/a/ODU5MTI3ODIxNTE5/submissions/by-status/and-sort-last-name/all?email%3Dmh116727@gmail.com&Email=mh116727@gmail.com>\n\nGoogle LLC 1600 Amphitheatre Parkway, Mountain View, CA 94043 USA\nThis email was sent to you because you indicated that you'd like to receive \nemail notifications from Google Classroom. If you don't want to receive \nemails like this, you can unsubscribe or change your settings \n<https://accounts.google.com/AccountChooser?continue=https://classroom.google.com/s?email%3Dmh116727@gmail.com&Email=mh116727@gmail.com>.", 'attachments': {}}
