2026-04-14 18:48:42,469 | INFO | app | Processing email 19d8bed14fb35c74 content: {'subject': 'Are you ready for AI-driven tech roles?', 'sender': 'Team Scaler <hello@scaler.com>', 'body': "Because the rules of engineering are already changing. \n\n \n \n\nEvery job description in tech is being rewritten by AI right now. AI isn't coming for your job, it's coming for the version of you that hasn't levelled up yet. Here's how we're making sure that's not you with our curriculum.\n\nThe engineers and data professionals edging ahead aren't just the \n ones using AI tools. They're the ones who understand systems deeply \nenough to know when AI gets it wrong\n.\n\nThat edge comes from unshakeable \nfundamentals, supercharged by AI fluency\n.\n\nThe best tech talent doesn't choose between \n foundations and AI. They master both. \n\nRepetitive tasks are automated, analytical grunt work is delegated \n to models. But what remains, and what commands a premium, is the \n engineer who can design systems, debug AI hallucinations, and \n architect solutions that no prompt alone can produce.\n\nThat's why we \nrebuilt every component of our curriculum from the ground up\n. Keeping the fundamentals that form the backbone of scalable tech while weaving AI-first thinking into every layer of the program.\n\nScaler's AI-First Curriculum is live. Whether you're starting out or levelling up, this is the program that puts you at the intersection of fundamentals and the future.\n\nBuilt for the next decade. Starting right now.\n\nTo stop receiving our emails - \nclick here", 'attachments': {}}
