2026-04-14 19:19:29,413 | INFO | app | Processing email 19d8b208abe63f38 content: {'subject': 'Due tomorrow: "Assignment (Unit–III)SSMDA"', 'sender': '"Swernima Suman (Classroom)" <no-reply@classroom.google.com>', 'body': "Notification settings \n<https://accounts.google.com/AccountChooser?continue=https://classroom.google.com/s?email%3Dmh116727@gmail.com&Email=mh116727@gmail.com>\n3rd year T15 \n<https://accounts.google.com/AccountChooser?continue=https://classroom.google.com/c/ODQxNDY4MTAxOTc5?email%3Dmh116727@gmail.com&Email=mh116727@gmail.com>\nDue tomorrow\n\nAssignment (Unit–III)SSMDA\n📄 Assignment (Unit–III)\n\nQ1.Define open set and closed set in a metric space.Also, prove that:The \ncomplement of an open set is closed.\n\nQ2. Define a metric space.\nVerify whether the function below defines a metric on ℝ:\nd(x, y) = |x\n\n - y|\n Q3. What is a Cauchy sequence?\n Prove that every convergent sequence is a Cauchy sequence in a metric \nspace.\n\nQ4. Explain the concept of compactness in a metric space.\nAlso, differentiate between:\nCompact set\nConnected set\nDue Apr 15\nView assignment \n<https://accounts.google.com/AccountChooser?continue=https://classroom.google.com/c/ODQxNDY4MTAxOTc5/a/ODE5MjU4NjU3OTk3/submissions/by-status/and-sort-last-name/all?email%3Dmh116727@gmail.com&Email=mh116727@gmail.com>\n\nGoogle LLC 1600 Amphitheatre Parkway, Mountain View, CA 94043 USA\nThis email was sent to you because you indicated that you'd like to receive \nemail notifications from Google Classroom. If you don't want to receive \nemails like this, you can unsubscribe or change your settings \n<https://accounts.google.com/AccountChooser?continue=https://classroom.google.com/s?email%3Dmh116727@gmail.com&Email=mh116727@gmail.com>.", 'attachments': {}}
