2026-04-14 19:21:16,987 | INFO | app | Processing email 19d8b19cccf2030a content: {'subject': 'Due tomorrow: "Assignment – Unit III (IT)"', 'sender': '"Swernima Suman (Classroom)" <no-reply@classroom.google.com>', 'body': "Notification settings \n<https://accounts.google.com/AccountChooser?continue=https://classroom.google.com/s?email%3Dmh116727@gmail.com&Email=mh116727@gmail.com>\n3rd year T15 \n<https://accounts.google.com/AccountChooser?continue=https://classroom.google.com/c/ODQxNDY4MTAxOTc5?email%3Dmh116727@gmail.com&Email=mh116727@gmail.com>\nDue tomorrow\n\nAssignment – Unit III (IT)\nAssignment – Unit III\nQ1.\nExplain the Project Time Management process. Describe all steps involved \nsuch as defining activities, sequencing, estimating resources & durations, \nand developing the schedule.\nQ2.\nWhat is a Project Schedule? Explain different techniques used for \nscheduling (like Gantt Chart, Network Diagram, Critical Path Method).\nQ3.\nDiscuss the importance of Project Cost Management. Explain the steps: cost \nestimation, budgeting, and cost control.\nQ4.\nDifferentiate between Time Management and Cost Management in a project. \nAlso explain how project management software helps in managing time and \ncost.\nDue Apr 15\nView assignment \n<https://accounts.google.com/AccountChooser?continue=https://classroom.google.com/c/ODQxNDY4MTAxOTc5/a/ODU5MTI3NzU1OTI5/submissions/by-status/and-sort-last-name/all?email%3Dmh116727@gmail.com&Email=mh116727@gmail.com>\n\nGoogle LLC 1600 Amphitheatre Parkway, Mountain View, CA 94043 USA\nThis email was sent to you because you indicated that you'd like to receive \nemail notifications from Google Classroom. If you don't want to receive \nemails like this, you can unsubscribe or change your settings \n<https://accounts.google.com/AccountChooser?continue=https://classroom.google.com/s?email%3Dmh116727@gmail.com&Email=mh116727@gmail.com>.", 'attachments': {}}
